<br>
Example:Divine Inspiration 15AC, 15 Wis, 15 Int, 35 Mana, Range Slot, CLR/DRU/SHM/NEC/WIZ/MAG/ENC<br>
<br>
Why can't it be 15AC, 15 Int, 35 Mana, NEC/WIZ/MAG/ENC? There are just to few Int caster only items.<br>
